unit tests -> tests each microservice functionality alone
component testing -> test each microservice with its datastores as a component
integration testing -> tests the communication between different microservices
end to end testing -> here the system is treated as a black box with request as input and response 
as output
performance testing(chaos engineering)
https://www.simform.com/blog/microservice-testing-strategies/


